==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Untreasured
<hw>Un*treas"ured</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<ety>[Properly p. p. of <ets>untreasure</ets>.]</ety> <def>Deprived of
treasure.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <ety>[Pref. <ets>un-</ets> not +
<ets>treasured</ets>.]</ety> <def>Not treasured; not kept as
treasure.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Untreatable</ent>⟦br⟧
